    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Chakra Control </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 2 (Spell Level 1)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 14 | <b>Successes:</b> 1</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 2 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 13</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You surround yourself with a thin layer of insulating Chakra to shield you from cold weather. If the outside temperature is between 40°F and 10°F (4°C and -12C°), you will not suffer any adverse effects of cold weather,and will feel as though the temperature was moderate.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> Each step decreases the minimum temperature at which this technique works by 2°F (-1°C), down to 0°F (-17°C).</p>\n",
